Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.69,0:00:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年芬兰…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是一大早的班会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一节课到第三节课又连着上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:02:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午休时间把贫血晕倒的学生送到家里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五节课时为了看有没有人翘课  一直在学校里巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后还因为吹奏乐大赛临近  要指导他们练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就变成这样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一天一直都站着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿健康凉鞋怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  对高一的学生来说我是很淑女的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索性把以前轻音部的事情挑明了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我是…  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不知道啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的教育啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍有破绽就会导致严重的后果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样的过去暴露的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们几个  快上课…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你高中时不也是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这也太穿越了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真接啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…干什么啊  突然打电话到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍…稍微等一下～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「干…干什么啊  突然打电话到这里来」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说起来  今天早上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  有那种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上开车把她送到学校  还吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后突然接到电话而大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来想  那人肯定是小佐和的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…唯学姐就不用去想了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是小孩子的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说曹操曹操到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊  那行为可疑的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她平时回去的方向不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小澪像侦探一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  跟上去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  这样做好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往左拐了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点跟上去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐最来劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  目标确认
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯重点监视右方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意不要被小佐和发现  并仔细观察其一举一动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗中监视吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.03,0:04:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好像很在意周围呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全陷进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她好像确实说过一个人很寂寞…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也有很多私事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多私事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的  我这方面可没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪确实是美女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:05:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅是女性  还有男性憧憬也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么会变成这种话题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别擅自推进下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别盯着我看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我对那种事情没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说  现在轻音就像是我的恋人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…为什么只打我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉  迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了别往学校打电话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:30.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是女性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  你就别多想了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是跟来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像电视剧一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这只女狐狸  今天就是制裁你的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被人家听见的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五位…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  能坐那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:05:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样穿着制服来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  把头低下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  再挤一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到对面去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  好过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再挤一下再挤一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  你就待那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要硬挤进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是安静一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  地点在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那个人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…五杯红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请使用那边的自动贩卖机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…办不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要这个巧克力蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就小律点好的  太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是没办法的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要南瓜精选布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这么令人心跳的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要奶油馅蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…被点掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点一样的东西不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  难得有这么多品种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  那么…  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:23.32,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（布丁帕露菲）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全忘了当初的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己点的记得自己付钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啊  被发现了就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  从刚刚开始是怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  很奇怪哦  一直在看着对面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘  嘘！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再好好考虑一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:07:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烦人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,含税1480日元…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零花钱全没了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你真吃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我可不想输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是不知道佐和子老师见的人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  你认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就是在以前的照片里和小佐和站在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DEATH DEVIL的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉丝汀娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  吓过头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这是常有的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是樱高轻音部的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这里也有个名侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们穿着制服带着吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为轻音部的学姐  有些话想和你们说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是部长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是澪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…请不要逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  用着很素雅的吉他嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹…弹得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定比佐和子老师弹得还好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前每天都和佐和子竞争吉他技巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不用客气  尽量点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  给她们追加果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  小纪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…小纪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好意思  我叫纪美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你不是外国人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自报姓名也稍晚了点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你们还有什么想吃的  不用客气尽管点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是个好人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么  我要雁拟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  雁拟是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  因为从没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得这名字很厉害吗  雁拟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:03.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（雁拟就是炸豆腐包，因味道像雁肉而得名，也叫飞龙头）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  有事要说是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是什么重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实佐和子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这是开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前轻音部的同期生要结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她希望我们在二次宴会上面演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只有佐和子一个人不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她在轻音部的事情是黑历史啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  雁拟  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象的要普通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你想象的是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来以为是浑身带刺的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑身带刺？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:11:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  擅自弹了这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  有哪里不对劲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天英语课自习
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持安静
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴吹同学给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪有什么想法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的乐队同伴都说不动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换了我们也不太可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说二次宴会上其他老师和新闻部的同学都会到场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化个妆挡一下怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但考虑到露馅的情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是  唯怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪的字好可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律怎么想  你是部长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我认真点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你画的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am a pen
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴吹同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…一开始的纸条是我传的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这不能怪小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问我可以出去罚站吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？可…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想罚站！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是「给我出去罚站」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从进小学开始12年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想终于实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我便没什么可留恋的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么梦想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  我摸到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也乐在其中的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说正经的  准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们啊  不记得昨天纪美小姐说的事情了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你们劝劝佐和子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但小佐和很固执啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没开始就打退堂鼓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么如果劝不回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劝不回来的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等着特训吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有这种事！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都忘光光了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特训的话会是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐的特训应该是些很辛苦的练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们又不是运动部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  换成轻音部的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  那就演奏到我能听到声音为止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但乐器…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐是靠灵魂演奏的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身心投入的话  就算没有乐器也能听到声音才对！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:51.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那放学后找她谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想站到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都给我进来继续自习
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意不要打扰到其他老师  小声一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:18.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和真有人气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不好上去求她了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的佐和子也很受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  特训是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你们说着玩的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.92,0:15:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是那样就见鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过希望你们能来帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有难度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你还没去洗澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  等下就去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心睡过头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  忧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  突然说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我长大后也能成为大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  要不要果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  佐和子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  不能上台
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当了老师实在是有很多不便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧  我们很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太～！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭  越来越恐怖了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我倒是挺喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐太过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  部长  接下来我要你从嘴里喷火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…做不到啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是陪伴新娘一同走过青春时代的友人乐团
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DEATH DEVIL为大家带来现场演出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外今天是特别编成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  那些孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  小唯  那把吉他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么啦  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家一起跟我们来狂欢吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  弹错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啦！真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思  从头来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为DEATH DEVIL是什么乐团呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实挺可爱的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油～DEATH DEVIL
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮你们打气哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打气？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:59.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DEATH DEVIL  DEATH DEVIL…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…DEATH DEVIL不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂间的激烈碰撞才是DEATH DEVIL的精髓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不行…我已经是一名教师了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的灵魂应该留在过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也对不住为我努力的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:12.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～抱歉  失败失败
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  DEATH DEVIL…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所追寻的DEATH DEVIL…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,献丑了  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DEATH DEVIL！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:21.36,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还希望大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是佐和子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子们  DEATH DEVIL不是这种软绵绵的音乐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就让你们见识一下真材实料！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK！来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:36.80,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘い言葉にご用心　WOW
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:39.37,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あんまそんなの慣れてない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:42.34,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かなり警戒注意報　WOW
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:44.98,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だけどどうやら裏がない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:51.36,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちょっと高めの理想論　WOW
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.79,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余裕ぶって見下ろして
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:56.73,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,できるつもりがムリして　WOW
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:59.24,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あぁ、強がって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:04.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計算してgetの予定　振りまわされfoil
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:07.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でも、恋に落ちちゃ　負けって嘘さ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:09.98,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当は負けじゃなーい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:13.13,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう、小悪魔より　誘惑より
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:16.17,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,マジで　マジで天使になりたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:18.87,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛の味はどんなっていうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:21.10,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もうすぐ分かりそう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:26.39,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,シンプルすぎるほど自分に正直な欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:32.23,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛の未来を頂だーい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:36.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}当心甜言蜜语　WOW
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:39.37,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}但还不太习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:42.34,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}非常警戒注意　WOW
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:44.98,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}却没居心不良
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:51.36,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}偏高的理想论　WOW
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.79,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}轻松俯瞰一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:56.73,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}错误估计的勉强　WOW
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:59.24,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}啊　还在逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:04.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}计算后get的预定　被摆弄的foil
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:07.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}但坠入爱河就输的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:09.98,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}其实并没有输
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:13.13,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}比起小恶魔和诱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:16.17,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}真的　真的更想成为天使
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:18.87,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}一直好奇的爱的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:21.10,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}马上就能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:26.39,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}给予单纯的自己坦诚的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:32.23,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}给我爱的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.66,0:21:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞砸了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你搞砸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我苦心营造的贤淑形象啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颜面尽失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  说到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  都怪小佐和你自己憋不住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过抱歉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和子老师在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的演出太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们期待着下次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来什么样的佐和子都那么受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  乐团不做到那种程度是不是就没法给人留下印象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  来吧！ 来给澪画个妆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想都别想！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒觉得挺不错～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐太过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.66,0:22:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊  我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.34,0:24:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热～


